snippet.title: Coming June 6th, 2024! | A Twisted Path To Renown
snippet.description:
A Twisted Path To Renown is coming to Steam on June 6th, 2024!

A Twisted Path To Renown is a new hardcore PvEvP extraction-based first-person shooter game, with deep and immersive survival mechanics and highly detailed crafting algorithms, set in 1899, United States.

Wishlist on STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2304660/a_twisted_path_to_renown/&utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=campaign
